| Bank Deposits | 5000000.00 | 2023-12-31 | 71662.08 | 2024-02-03 |

The initial value of Bank Deposits as of 2023-12-31 is 5000000.00.
The end value of Bank Deposits as of 2024-02-03 is 71662.08.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '5000000.00', 'end value': '71662.08'}}
```
